CHMP04.title: The Experiment
CHMP04.description: Sharron is met at an airport whilst on holiday by Major Cranmore who invites her to a large house apparently to pit her super-human skills against a like-minded - literally - group of people in a series of tests.

FWLT01.path: ../Fawlty Towers/Fawlty Towers - 01 A Touch of Class.mp4
FWLT01.title: A Touch of Class
FWLT01.description: Basil is delighted when a member of the aristocracy chooses to stay at the Fawlty Towers, snubbing the normal guests who frequent the hotel.

SPRA01.title: The Great Plan - Part 1
SPRA01.description: Speed Racer enters his first race to win money for his family. Meanwhile, a gang of robbers are after Pops's secret plans... which he hid in the windshield of Speed's car.

SPRA03.path: ../Speed Racer/Speed Racer - 03 Challenge of the Masked Racer (part 1, SD).m4v
SPRA03.title: Challenge of the Masked Racer - Part 1
SPRA03.description: Speed's first encounter with Racer X, a mysterious masked driver who is rumored to cause car crashes whenever he races.

SPRA05.title: The Secret Engine - Part 1
SPRA05.description: Spee tries to help an old man find his stolen car. It turns out the car has a map to a treasure, which a criminal mastermind is prepared to get at any cost.

HONW02.title: The Owl and the Eye
HONW02.path: ../Honey West/Honey West 02 - The Owl and the Eye.mp4
HONW02.description: Honey and Sam are hired by a art museum's insurance company to prove how easy it is to bypass its security measures. After proving the insurance company's point, the private investigators agree to furnish an elaborate new system - which is promptly evaded by art thieves.

HONW04.title: A Matter of Wife and Death
HONW04.path: ../Honey West/Honey West 04 - A Matter of Wife and Death.mp4
HONW04.description: Honey tries to protect a woman executive who has received numerous death threats.

ZATV01.title: A Challenge of Chance
ZATV01.description: Two Bosses fight for control of a mine. Will Zatoichi takes sides? A man with a musket wants to end that threat.

LISP01.title: The Reluctant Stowaway
LISP01.path: ../Lost in Space/Lost in Space - 01 The Reluctant Stowaway.m4v
LISP01.description: The Jupiter 2 is to launch, but a saboteur wants to destroy it. Unfortunately he is part of the Jupiter 2 crew now Lost In Space.

LISP03.title: Island in the Sky
LISP03.path: ../Lost in Space/Lost in Space - 03 Island in the Sky.m4v
LISP03.description: While spacewalking Doctor Robinson is pulled down onto a planet. Major West lands the ship to search for him.

LOTL01.path: ../Land of the Lost/Land of the Lost - 01 Cha Ka.mp4
LOTL01.title: Cha-Ka
LOTL01.description: Will and Holly save a Pakuni ape-boy named Cha-Ka from Grumpy the Tyrannosaurus Rex.

48833173.title: Where is Everybody?
48833173.description: Mike Ferris finds himself alone in the small Oakwood town and without recollection about his name, where he is or who he is. Mike wanders through the town trying to find a living soul. The tension increases and Mike has a breakdown.

SOKO01.title: Dracolon: The Great Sea Monster
SOKO01.path: ../Johnny Sokko/Johnny Sokko - 01 Dracolon, The Great Sea Monster.m4v
SOKO01.description: Shipwrecked, Daisaku (Johnny Sokko) and Juro Minami (an agent for Unicorn) drift to an island and are captured by the BF gang. The island is in fact, a base of the B.F. gang. They happen to discover a huge robot while they are running away.

DNMN01.title: Yesterday's Enemies
DNMN01.description: Brett is known to be giving away British industrial secrets. However, when Drake confronts him, he discovers things are a lot more complicated and that Brett is not the only person being investigated.

SOKO03.title: The Gargoyle Vine: A Space Plant
SOKO03.description: Under Emperor Guillotine's orders, Dr. Over, a leading member of BF Syndicate, comes to the earth with a fossil of a devilish space plant called Satan Rose.

028F33BF.title: One for the Angels
028F33BF.path: ../Twilight Zone/Twilight Zone - 002 One for the Angels.mp4
028F33BF.description: A pitchman is visited by Mr. Death and is forced to get his priorities in order.

ULTR02.title: Shoot the Invaders!
ULTR02.description: The Balatans have come to Earth to make a new home, at the expense of Earth's inhabitants.

ULTR04.title: Five Seconds Before the Explosion
ULTR04.description: A nuclear bomb has gone missing and winds up being stuck to a lizard-like monster. This monster is bent on ruining Fuji's vacation.

CHMP01.title: The Beginning
CHMP01.description: Sharron MacReady, Craig Stirling and Richard Barrett work as agents for international law enforcement bureau Nemesis, based in Geneva, Whilst returning from a mission in China with bacteriological material stolen from the Chinese, their plane is shot down over the Himalayas.

CHMP03.title: Reply Box No. 666
CHMP03.description: A young explosives expert called Semenkin is found murdered in his Jamaican hotel room whilst posing as a French businessman.

CSCR01.title: The Mysterons
CSCR01.description: After a misunderstanding on the planet Mars, a war is started between humans and an alien race called The Mysterons. Thier first act of revenge is to try and assassinate The World President.

7UP01.title: Seven Up!
7UP01.description: A group of British children aged 7 from widely ranging backgrounds are interviewed about a range of subjects.

CHMP05.title: Happening
CHMP05.description: The Champions are Down Under and Richard has infiltrated a terrorist group who have planted a radioactive device in the Simpson Desert.

SRVR01.title: The Fourth Horseman
SRVR01.description: A strange disease sweeps through Britain and the world with amazing swiftness. Abby Grant searches for her son. Jenny thrust out of her city life wanders through the country around London trying to find a way to survive.

AHCP002.title: Premonition
AHCP002.description: A man returning to his home town finds his father has died, and suspects his friends are covering up the true details of that death.

SPRA02.path: ../Speed Racer/Speed Racer - 02 The Great Plan (part 2, SD).m4v
SPRA02.title: The Great Plan - Part 2
SPRA02.description: Speed continues his race, and the robbers continue their attempts to capture Speed.

AHCP003.title: Trigger in Leash
AHCP003.path: ../Alfred Hitchcock Presents/Alfred Hitchcock Presents 003 - Trigger In Leash.m4v
AHCP003.description: A cook tries everything she can think of to end a dispute between two gunmen who have sworn to kill each other.

JOQU01.title: The Mystery of the Lizard Men
JOQU01.description: A foreign power uses the Sargasso Sea to conduct laser experiments and employs "lizard men" to scare away potential interlopers.

SPRA04.path: ../Speed Racer/Speed Racer - 04 Challenge of the Masked Racer (part 2).mp4
SPRA04.title: Challenge of the Masked Racer - Part 2
SPRA04.description: Speed Racer and Racer X participate in the Trans-Country race... as well as competitors who stoop to dirty tricks to get rid of them.

TWZN003.title: Mr. Denton on Doomsday
TWZN003.path: ../Twilight Zone/Twilight Zone - 003 Mr. Denton on Doomsday.mp4
TWZN003.description: The town drunk in the old-west faces his past when Fate lends a hand.

TWZN004.title: The Sixteen Millimeter Shrine
TWZN004.path: ../Twilight Zone/Twilight Zone - 004 The Sixteen Millimeter Shrine.mp4
TWZN004.description: Barbara Jean Trenton is a faded film star who lives in the past by constantly re-watching her old movies instead of moving on with her life, so her associates try to lure her out of her self-imposed isolation.

HONW03.title: The Abominable Snowman
HONW03.description: When a dying client gives Honey a snowglobe, the private detective doesn't grasp the importance of the object until other interested parties attempt to steal it.

AHCP001.title: Revenge
AHCP001.description: When Carl Spann's wife Elsa is assaulted by an unknown attacker, he drives his still-incoherent wife around town, hoping she can point him out, so he can kill him.

HONW01.path: ../Honey West/Honey West 01 - The Swingin' Mrs. Jones.mp4
HONW01.title: The Swingin' Mrs. Jones
HONW01.description: After losing her client's $50,000 and getting a knock on the head in the bargain, Honey West is more determined than ever to break up a blackmail ring that preys on wealthy middle-aged women.

HONW05.title: Live a Little, Kill a Little
HONW05.path: ../Honey West/Honey West 05 - Live a Little, Kill a Little.mp4
HONW05.description: When the sister of a prominent businessman breaks off a relationship with a local mobster, Honey and an assassin race to be the first to find her.

AHCP005.title: Into Thin Air
AHCP005.path: ../Alfred Hitchcock Presents/Alfred Hitchcock Presents 005 - Into Thin Air.m4v
AHCP005.description: When a young woman leaves her ill mother in a Paris hotel room and comes back later, she finds her mother is missing, and all the hotel's employees deny she and her mother were ever there.

PRSN01.title: The Arrival
PRSN01.description: After resigning, a secret agent finds himself trapped in a bizarre prison known only as The Village.

AHCP004.title: Don't Come Back Alive
AHCP004.path: ../Alfred Hitchcock Presents/Alfred Hitchcock Presents 004 - Don't Come Back Alive.m4v
AHCP004.description: Frank Partridge and his wife plot to cheat their life insurance company by having her hide out for 7 years and declared legally dead, but an investigator believes Mr. Partridge has murdered her.

LISP00.title: No Place to Hide (Pilot)
LISP00.description: The Robinsons, Earth's first family of outer space, head to colonize Alpha Centauri in their flying saucer, the Gemini 12, but crash land on an uncharted planet where they deal with its challenges and dangers.

TWZN005.title: Walking Distance
TWZN005.description: A man travels back in time to his childhood, arriving just a few miles away from his native town.

LISP02.title: The Derelict
LISP02.path: ../Lost in Space/Lost in Space - 02 The Derelict.m4v
LISP02.description: The Jupiter 2 is pulled into a giant ship occupied by bubble-like creatures.

CON101.title: The Trigger Effect
CON101.description: One thing leads to another and our dependence on technology. A New York City Blackout serves as example.

SOKO02.title: Nucleon: The Magic Globe
SOKO02.path: ../Johnny Sokko/Johnny Sokko - 02 Nucleon, The Magic Globe.m4v
SOKO02.description: Emperor Guillotine, king of BF syndicate, plans to take back Giant Robot and to arrest Daisaku (Johhny Sokko), the only one that can give orders to the robot. He sends a huge magic metal globe called Glober to the earth.

DWHO0751.title: Robot (part 1)
DWHO0751.description: Can the Doctor, now in his fourth incarnation, recover from his post-regenerative trauma to save the Earth from Think Tank and their plot for world domination?

SOKO04.title: Monster Ligon-Tyrox: A Strange Monster
SOKO04.description: Emperor Guillotine sends Dr. Over and Ligon, a new weapon in the shape of a pyramid, to the earth. By operating Ligon, Over destroys oil fields in Araia one after another.

DWHO0752.title: Robot (part 2)
DWHO0752.description: The Doctor and Sarah become convinced Think Tank are behind the electronic component thefts but are unable to stop them carrying out another raid.

ULTR01.title: Ultra Operation No. 1
ULTR01.description: Ultraman is escorting his prisoner to its final destination. The prisoner escapes and heads toward Earth. As Ultraman follows in pursuit, he accidentally crashes into an Earth craft, injuring its pilot and altering both of their lives forever.

ULTR03.title: Science Patrol, Move Out!
ULTR03.description: An invisible monster that thrives on electricity begins destroying power plants in Japan.

DWHO0753.title: Robot (part 3)
DWHO0753.description: Sarah and Kettlewell infiltrate an SRS meeting to try and find out what Miss Winters is up to but there is a surprise in store.

DWHO0761.path: ../Doctor Who/Dr. Who 076 - The Ark In Space 1.m4v
DWHO0761.title: The Ark in Space (part 1)
DWHO0761.description: The Doctor's attempt to give Harry a trip in the TARDIS sees the two of them and Sarah arriving onboard a space station in the far future, with some rather deadly security mechanisms.

KNFU00.title: The Way of the Tiger, the Sign of the Dragon
KNFU00.description: After avenging the death of his teacher, a Shaolin monk flees China to the American West and helps people while being pursued by bounty hunters.

ULTR05.title: The Secret of the Miroganda
ULTR05.description: A scientist finds a rare plant that is determined to destroy humanity.

DWHO0754.title: Robot (part 4)
DWHO0754.description: UNIT attempt to get into the bunker to stop Miss Winters setting off the world's nuclear missiles but first they have to get past the K1.

CHMP02.title: The Invisible Man
CHMP02.description: Surgeon John Hallam has perfected an 'invisible man', a device which is transplanted into the ear and 'tells' people to obey instructions.
